Package: autoclaw
Version: 0.1.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: git, libc6
Maintainer: Autoclaw Team <team@autoclaw.dev>
Description: Self-improving AI experiment loop for Claude Cowork
 Autoclaw is a no-code automation loop that lets Claude (or any LLM)
 iteratively improve code against a user-defined rubric. Human edits
 context.md; AI edits train.py; every experiment is a git commit.
Homepage: https://autoclaw.dev
